<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight: normal'><u>BeagleBoard.org Trademark Usage Guidelines<o:p></o:p></u></b></p>
<p class=MsoNormal><o:p> </o:p></p>
<p class=MsoNormal>The BeagleBoard.org Foundation is dedicated to providing education in and promotion of the design and use of open-source software and hardware in embedded computing. As part of this, we provide open-source software (e.g., firmware and/or operating system source code) and open-source hardware designs (e.g., schematics and PCB layouts) for our devices. </p>
<p class=MsoNormal><o:p> </o:p></p>
<p class=MsoNormal>The BeagleBoard.org Foundation owns each of the trademarks shown below (the “Trademarks”). A license from the BeagleBoard.org Foundation is required if you want to use any of these logos. License eligibility requirements are discussed in detail below. Please contact Christine Long (<a href="mailto:christi@beagleboard.org">christi@beagleboard.org</a>) if you are interested in obtaining a license and/or have any questions regarding these trademarks. </p>
<p class=MsoNormal><o:p> </o:p></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight: normal'><u>Usage Restrictions<o:p></o:p></u></b></p>
<p class=MsoNormal><o:p> </o:p></p>
<p class=MsoNormal>Third party use of the Trademarks is only permitted as indicated below. You may not use any of these trademarks without written approval from the BeagleBoard.org Foundation.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes"> </span></p>
<p class=MsoNormal><o:p> </o:p></p>
<table class=MsoNormalTable border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 style='border-collapse:collapse;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:0in 0in 0in 0in'> <thead> <tr style='mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes;page-break-inside:avoid'> <td width=152 valign=top style='width:151.95pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt; background:#D9D9D9;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'> <p class=MsoNormal><b>Mark<o:p></o:p></b></p> </td> <td width=315 valign=top style='width:315.05pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left:none;background:#D9D9D9;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'> <p class=MsoNormal><b>Requirements<o:p></o:p></b></p> </td> </tr> </thead> <tr style='mso-yfti-irow:1;page-break-inside:avoid'> <td width=152 valign=top style='width:151.95pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top:none;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'> <p class=MsoNormal>“BeagleBoard.org” (logo)</p> <p class=MsoNormal>“BeagleBoard.org” (text)</p> <p class=MsoNormal><o:p> </o:p></p> </td> <td width=315 valign=top style='width:315.05pt;border-top:none;border-left: none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'> <p class=MsoNormal>These trademarks are reserved for official products of BeagleBoard.org, such as the BeagleBoard and BeagleBone product families. Use of these trademarks is reserved for a select group of products and contractual partners of BeagleBoard.org.</p> <p class=MsoNormal><o:p> </o:p></p> </td> </tr> <tr style='mso-yfti-irow:2;page-break-inside:avoid'> <td width=152 valign=top style='width:151.95pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top:none;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'> <p class=MsoNormal>“BeagleBoard” (text)</p> </td> <td width=315 valign=top style='width:315.05pt;border-top:none;border-left: none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'> <p class=MsoNormal>The “BeagleBoard” trademark refers to a product family of BeagleBoard.org. Use of this trademark is reserved for a select group of contractual partners of BeagleBoard.org that manufacture/distribute the BeagleBoard line of products.</p> <p class=MsoNormal><o:p> </o:p></p> </td> </tr> <tr style='mso-yfti-irow:3;page-break-inside:avoid'> <td width=152 valign=top style='width:151.95pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top:none;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'> <p class=MsoNormal>“BeagleBone” (text)</p> </td> <td width=315 valign=top style='width:315.05pt;border-top:none;border-left: none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'> <p class=MsoNormal>The “BeagleBone” trademark refers to a product family of BeagleBoard.org. Use of this trademark is reserved for a select group of contractual partners of BeagleBoard.org that manufacture/distribute the BeagleBone line of products.</p> <p class=MsoNormal><o:p> </o:p></p> </td> </tr> <tr style='mso-yfti-irow:4;page-break-inside:avoid'> <td width=152 valign=top style='width:151.95pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top:none;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'> <p class=MsoNormal>“BeagleBoard Compliant” logo</p> <p class=MsoNormal><o:p> </o:p></p> </td> <td width=315 valign=top style='width:315.05pt;border-top:none;border-left: none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'> <p class=MsoNormal>This trademark is intended for a circuit board that is manufactured using an un-modified version of an open-source hardware design for an official product of BeagleBoard.org (e.g., a product from the BeagleBoard or BeagleBone product families).
